{"tid":565543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港大部份廢老都冇乜點捱過 可以串鳩佢","createTime":"2018-02-19T05:32:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T03:51:17.000Z","uid":4493,"like":115,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"51610c449fc2a317060866869a7a55bcb7147cbf","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>對住後輩，老屎忽總會扮自己獅子山精神，靠努力成為成功人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n事實上當年真係獅子山精神而成功嘅人，有一大半已經移咗民，順利成為英國加拿大美國澳洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反有好多所謂香港人，其實係七八十年代由支那走來香港。呢一班人裏面唔少係打輸咗嘅紅衛兵，罪犯等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時嘅真香港人天真又好人，通常都會幫佢哋搵工搵地方住，令佢哋唔使捱直接享受已經經濟發達的香港嘅福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後前途危機出現移民潮，出現大量中高層職位空缺，新香港人快速上位！<br />\n<br />\n呢班支那人實際上又無料又賤格，結果香港快速仆街，成為而家嘅人間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n結論：廢老就係廢閪支那人，靠僥倖先至上到位，所以最驚有料嘅後生仔，要成日踩柒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「敬老」係佢哋最後嘅武器，對住全無道德的支那人絕對唔使客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac3acbf156b93d518ccdecd68850bb5740c94b46","tid":565543,"uid":10894,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f1cdc475914df5ea7bf6d10e0dac078192e4d2f3","tid":565543,"uid":162424,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"913a8c58a66340cbc21cda2c7cf1bf1b88a26ac9","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"ac3acbf156b93d518ccdecd68850bb5740c94b46","tid":565543,"uid":10894,"like":4,"dislike":24,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:35:31.000Z",