:51.000Z","msg":"反而西方傳統名校教出來嘅人做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e3a79c63c603ab882ce05651a1f25daa11ed730","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T10:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8aed0df180014544fe775a661dfab0a80193c9","tid":565543,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:09:38.000Z","msg":"戰後出世呢班邊有涯過"},{"pid":"bd176b7adb947ca7709e9800c4b463b9bac78d60","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9b8aed0df180014544fe775a661dfab0a80193c9","tid":565543,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:09:38.000Z","msg":"戰後出世呢班邊有涯過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"1945-55都叫涯過 50年代香港好撚窮又危險<br />\n但開口埋口廢青嗰啲多數係之後出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da56c208d9c512236346bee80266c69652d9632","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa2dad2ef327b831dc2a7be52857c3d1281d09c","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba01b03509c3d46cc2ba7119d047ba99ad96654","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"做嘢點唔洗捱？訓係度有錢收？上位之前你都要入到去坐低做嘢。"},{"pid":"6e171105de85747c69eedd0ba5a5caabc041671b","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b32606d994cdbd8239e9626c517423a6bf083fb1","tid":565543,"uid":130398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51610c449fc2a317060866869a7a55bcb7147cbf","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>對住後輩，老屎忽總會扮自己獅子山精神，靠努力成為成功人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n事實上當年真係獅子山精神而成功嘅人，有一大半已經移咗民，順利成為英國加拿大美國澳洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反有好多所謂香港人，其實係七八十年代由支那走來香港。呢一班人裏面唔少係打輸咗嘅紅衛兵，罪犯等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時嘅真香港人天真又好人，通常都會幫佢哋搵工搵地方住，令佢哋唔使捱直接享受已經經濟發達的香港嘅福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後前途危機出現移民潮，出現大量中高層職位空缺，新香港人快速上位！<br />\n<br />\n呢班支那人實際上又無料又賤格，結果香港快速仆街，成為而家嘅人間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n結論：廢老就係廢閪支那人，靠僥倖先至上到位，所以最驚有料嘅後生仔，要成日踩柒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「敬老」係佢哋最後嘅武器，對住全無道德的支那人絕對唔使客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"佢地食住港英七八十年代既盛世   主要功勞都冇佢哋份   到依家就扮老屎忽 屌我哋啲90後廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"你都癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩盛世都好，財富都要當下的人去勞動賺取，唔係政府免費pay俾你。<br />\n<br />\n四季風調雨順，你唔落地耕田，塊地一樣都係得草冇收成。<br />\n<br />\n當時D人又勤力去做，付出佢哋的勞力，你憑咩話人冇功勞。"},{"pid":"5d6ac38811833ce3e5dc87dc28110c2a19606ea8","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf242171475aa7560c3af352a141cf3cec0e8129","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1d4998b385f82c1881c7bdf3d04693836170b8ec","tid":565543,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:10:14.000Z","msg":"但以前啲工真係辛苦嘅，但又未必代表而家唔辛苦喎<br />\n同埋我覺得佢地做埋做埋咪又係上繳被老闆吸血<br />\n<br />\n以前嗰班老闆根本好醒<br />\n無論做工程定炒野<br />\n佢地收得好高，咁啲人有錢咪肯科水<br />\n普通奴工以為自己得到嘅野好好<br />\n就算判工程做，佢都係接判交畀人做<br />\n自己就過河濕腳又唔洗做<br />\n個收入應該係普通奴工嘅幾倍<br />\n其實嗰時開始個經濟實力已經拉開左<br />\n而嗰啲奴工簡單講就係冇做生涯規劃<br />\n可能攞晒去賭錢<br />\n呢度如果當踢波人地上半場喺到積累財富<br />\n人地上左岸再賭都得啦<br />\n奴工就一開始攞去賭"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T06:31:36.000Z","msg":"工程就可能係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但嗰個年代好多人返本地公司，嗰時唔係間間要大學學位，上頭經理移民就要升人上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係話佢哋全部不勞而獲，但係機會同埋際遇肯定好過宜家好多，絕對無資格話依家啲後生仔廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嗰時只要正正常常返工，幾年之後買樓，到今日生活已經過得好過一半香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四五十歲嗰啲真係以為而家大學生做幾年野可以上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:56:41.000Z","msg":"而家好多90後都係正正常常返工，做十年八載，人工點都兩三萬，三十幾歲搵個差唔多的老婆就買樓供樓，過多幾十年都一樣，變左老嘢，即係同你而家睇而家咁。<br />\n<br />\n一樣都可以過緊而家的生活。"},{"pid":"7c12bc802ac7638ae8dee163e7d3a8e5bb1d488c","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ba01b03509c3d46cc2ba7119d047ba99ad96654","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"做嘢點唔洗捱？訓係度有錢收？上位之前你都要入到去坐低做嘢。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"我識一個阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n八字頭好景入中型港企，好快過萬糧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n炒樓炒股(必升年代)，再上位做老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家一日蛇幾粒鐘，可以由中環蛇去荃灣搵我地食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502351feb0504a5992350eb6ec76615445d24a4d","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad89fbafa5688a67dfe520a75d9af889ef3056d","tid":565543,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor