ote":{"pid":"6e171105de85747c69eedd0ba5a5caabc041671b","tid":565543,"uid":53223,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b32606d994cdbd8239e9626c517423a6bf083fb1","tid":565543,"uid":130398,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"51610c449fc2a317060866869a7a55bcb7147cbf","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>對住後輩，老屎忽總會扮自己獅子山精神，靠努力成為成功人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n事實上當年真係獅子山精神而成功嘅人，有一大半已經移咗民，順利成為英國加拿大美國澳洲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反有好多所謂香港人，其實係七八十年代由支那走來香港。呢一班人裏面唔少係打輸咗嘅紅衛兵，罪犯等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時嘅真香港人天真又好人，通常都會幫佢哋搵工搵地方住，令佢哋唔使捱直接享受已經經濟發達的香港嘅福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後前途危機出現移民潮，出現大量中高層職位空缺，新香港人快速上位！<br />\n<br />\n呢班支那人實際上又無料又賤格，結果香港快速仆街，成為而家嘅人間地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n結論：廢老就係廢閪支那人，靠僥倖先至上到位，所以最驚有料嘅後生仔，要成日踩柒佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「敬老」係佢哋最後嘅武器，對住全無道德的支那人絕對唔使客氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"佢地食住港英七八十年代既盛世   主要功勞都冇佢哋份   到依家就扮老屎忽 屌我哋啲90後廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T02:51:50.000Z","msg":"你都癡線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咩盛世都好，財富都要當下的人去勞動賺取，唔係政府免費pay俾你。<br />\n<br />\n四季風調雨順，你唔落地耕田，塊地一樣都係得草冇收成。<br />\n<br />\n當時D人又勤力去做，付出佢哋的勞力，你憑咩話人冇功勞。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">當時D人又勤力去做，付出佢哋的勞力</span><br />\n<br />\n你講出重點<br />\n邊個辛苦D邊個勤力D我唔敢斷言，因為呢樣野好主觀<br />\n但起碼以前勤力完係有回報<br />\n而家你日日做十幾粒鐘都仲係買唔到樓"},{"pid":"44051ecad65d6110808e336519ef82580eb2a92e","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n但起碼以前勤力完係有回報<br />\n而家你日日做十幾粒鐘都仲係買唔到樓</blockquote><br />\n係 至少以前OT無咁普遍 除咗返工仲可以做其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3371867a53b9c6e3d5727a412c7d4e9b905d5625","tid":565543,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"游水落黎個班<br />\n死左幾多個你唔知啫"},{"pid":"fe2557291c87b3a75ce27e097e19a4390d88fc24","tid":565543,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"20125bdf30bba1817d424c57e9fd0e10f1d8e3e9","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe2557291c87b3a75ce27e097e19a4390d88fc24","tid":565543,"uid":86841,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:55:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"企開啲啦JR我屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你冇其他五毛屎都不如呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老伯父都有料過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba74d47b673bb1dd63ec96c5dedd7d8c8c0c152","tid":565543,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3371867a53b9c6e3d5727a412c7d4e9b905d5625","tid":565543,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:54:37.000Z","msg":"游水落黎個班<br />\n死左幾多個你唔知啫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:10:23.000Z","msg":"請重讀原文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n七八十年代仲玩游水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a2dcc4ef0ff9c260d79e41ad